  "body": "I try to write codes as below to calculate the position of value of mapping ( `keccak256(k . p)` ) described at [Layout of State Variables in Storage](https://solidity.readthedocs.io/en/develop/miscellaneous.html#layout-of-state-variables-in-storage).\r\nBut both results are different with position show in debugger.\r\nCould you point what mistake I make?\r\nThanks.\r\n\r\n` byte32 pos = keccak256(uint256(k),'.',uint256(p));`\r\nand \r\n```\r\n        bytes memory byteArr = new bytes(32 + 1 +32);\r\n        bytes32 bytesK = bytes32(uint256(k));\r\n        for (uint i = 0; i < 32; i++) {\r\n            byteArr[i] = bytesK[i];\r\n        }\r\n        byteArr[32] = byte('.');\r\n        bytes32 bytesP = bytes32(uint256(p));\r\n        for (uint j = 0; j < 32; j++) {\r\n            byteArr[33 + j] = bytesP[j];\r\n        }\r\n        byte32 pos = keccak256(byteArr);\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n",
